00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.400
Project: 22 Repainted and Refinished Kitchen Island

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:21.133
Remove all hardware and sand all paintable surfaces until smooth. Wipe clean.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:34.333
Mask off countertop.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:51.666
Apply a light coat of Krylon ColorMaster primer to all paintable surface to further improve adhesion and provide added durability.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:58.800
Coat all paintable surfaces of the island with Krylon ColorMaster paint.

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:20.066
Coat all paintable surfaces of the drawers and cabinet doors with Krylon ColorMaster paint.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:38.666
Once all pieces are dry to handle - about 1 hour - reattach all hardware and replace all drawers and cabinet doors.

